	[1113257] = L"But I'm so close! If I can just talk to the right people we'll be in business for sure!",
	[1048149] = L"The 'Visual Aid' window shows you pictorial information regarding your current quest objective.  You can move the window around and position it anywhere you like. <BR><BR> Right clicking anywhere on the window closes it.  To re-open the Visual Aid window, you can open your quest log via the 'View Quest Log' or  'Show Visual Aid' context menu on your avatar.",
