	[1113478] = L"You've inversed the state of your gem. You must neutralize it!",
	[1113479] = L"Hello again!<br><br>This is Part II of my experiment. Beyond these doors is a challenge for those carrying an Experimental Gem.",
	[1113480] = L"INSTRUCTIONS:<br><br>Activate the Gem to start the self-destruct timer. You have 30 minutes to reach the final room.",
	[1113481] = L"Each room has colored areas matching various states:<br>White = Cold <br>Pink = Warm <br>Blue = Freezing<br>Red = Blazing",
	[1113482] = L"Green = Poison<br>Orange = Cure<br>Dark Green= Lethal<br>Brown=Greater Cure<br><br>Your gem's state will cycle randomly through these",
	[1113483] = L"colors. Each time the gem shifts, you must enter the colored region that will bring your gem back to neutral state (grey). ",
	[1113484] = L"Failing when the gem reaches the extreme of any state get you expelled from the room and you will have to start over. The self-destruct",
	[1113485] = L"timer will not reset.<br><br>Once you reach the final room, place your gem in the box to receive your reward.",
