	[1113499] = L"In the Weeds",
	[1113500] = L"Help Farmer Nash find his pitchfork by pulling the weeds in his garden until you uncover it.  (Pull weeds by double clicking them)  When you find it, return it to him for your reward. <br><center>-----</center><br>I hate to trouble you, but sometimes a problem needs a plow and sometimes it needs a sword.  I am good with a plow, but terrible with a sword.<br><br>I have been plagued with a strange weed for some time.  Every day I have to clean them out of my garden and carry them away with my pitch fork.  Yesterday I was working there and\x2026 well, I must have nodded off because when I woke my pitchfork was gone!<br><br>I have heard talk of thieves who seek treasure in the sacred tomb, but I really don\x2019t think they took my pitchfork, in fact I think it just got lost in the weeds!<br><br>I would find it myself, but now that we are so close to the edge of the world, many wild creatures are lurking about and some might be hiding in these weeds.  I\x2019ve seen the creatures that have been roaming these parts recently and I fear for my life!  The problem is, if I don\x2019t get my crop in the ground soon, we won\x2019t make it through the winter.  Will you help?",
	[1113501] = L"I understand.  I certainly don\x2019t want you to do something you don\x2019t want to do.",
	[1113502] = L"Did you find my pitchfork?  I'm sure it is under those weeds somewhere.  It was a gift from King Draxinusom when he assigned me this job, I can\x2019t bear to lose it!",
	[1113503] = L"Oh, thank you!  Here is your reward as promised.  I will get right back to work in a few minutes.",
