	[1113960] = L"Which set of User Settings would you like to use? This will affect targeting and chat.",
	[1113961] = L"Use the Enhanced Client's default settings.",
	[1113962] = L"Use the Classic Client's default settings.",
	[1113963] = L"Do not change my current settings.",
	[1113964] = L"Some setup is required below.",
	[1113965] = L"Reset to Enhanced Client default key bindings",
	[1113966] = L"Reset to Classic Client default key bindings<br>(recommended for Legacy Chat Mode)",
	[1113967] = L"Your naughty twin steals some of your candy.",
	[1113968] = L"Dear Tomas,<br><br>Jared has not returned home since he last went to work in his lab 2 days ago. As you know, he had been working on a special project. His behaviour changed greatly as his project progressed. I have turned every stone but no ",
	[1113969] = L"one seems to know where he might be. I\x2019m worried sick. Any information or insight you may have would be greatly appreciated.<br><br>The bearer of this letter is assisting us in the search. Please share any information you have, however trivial it seems.",
	[1113970] = L"Help on locating his secret lab would be especially welcomed.<br><br>Sincerely, <br><br>Eliza",
	[1113971] = L"Your naughty twin turns you into a pile of maggots. Yuck!",
	[1113972] = L"Your naughty twin teleports you away with a naughty laugh!",
	[1113973] = L"I am sorry, but I cannot discuss with anyone not officially on this case. If you have proof that you are, please provide it!",
	[1113974] = L"Ah! Eliza sent you! Of course, I will assist any way I can. Ask me any question.",
	[1113975] = L"Black Cat Statuette",
	[1113976] = L"a torn note",
	[1113977] = L"You pick up a piece of torn parchment.",
	[1113978] = L"You swiftly reassemble the note. It's still legible!",
	[1113979] = L"a letter from Eliza",
	[1113980] = L"a note from Isham",
	[1113981] = L"My Love,<br><br>I am sorry I had to postpone our rendez-vous again. But this time it\x2019s truly worth it! That tinker Jared will be giving me a lot of money just to help him test children toys for Hallows\x2019 Eve! You should come as well! Maybe",
	[1113982] = L"we can convince him he needs an extra helper and you could make some gold too. And then we would have enough to elope like we always wanted!<br><br>The lab is well hidden and the guard won\x2019t let you in without permission so bring this note as he may ask",
	[1113983] = L"for it. In one of the caves at the mining camp north from here, you\x2019ll find a big grey skull. Say \x201cloki\x201d near the skull and it will take you to me. <br><br>See you soon!<br><br>Isham",
	[1113984] = L"Population",
	[1113985] = L"lit",
	[1113986] = L"not lit",
	[1113987] = L"You light the Jack-O-Lantern",
	[1113988] = L"You extinguish the Jack-O-Lantern",
	[1113989] = L"soul harvester",
	[1113990] = L"murky morph potion",
	[1113991] = L"It would be safer not to drink it until you know what it does. The Hag might have some insight.",
	[1113992] = L"You take a sample of the mixture and put it in your backpack.",
	[1113993] = L"Jared",
	[1113994] = L"DAY 1<br>I finally managed to get the Hag's morph recipe. I'm eager to see if it works as well as I hope. If I succeed, Tomas will be so proud of me! He will be blown away!",
	[1113995] = L"DAY 2<br>I retained the services of Leto and Carl to be the first testers. Something went wrong. They morphed as was intended but I can't bring them back to their human form.",
	[1113996] = L"skeleton halloween costume",
	[1113997] = L"DAY 3<br>Sam and Laura drank some of my modified potion. It almost worked. I'm close, I can feel it! Leto and Carl are getting worse though. They're growling like beasts...",
	[1113998] = L"DAY 4<br>Leto and Carl are gone. They don't seem to have a shred of humanity left. Sam and Laura will be the same soon. How did it come to this? Isham volunteered to help. He needs the ",
	[1113999] = L"money to elope with his belle. I shouldn't but I'm so close! And if I succeed, it will surely also help bring back the others to their original form. I cannot give up now.",
	[1114000] = L"DAY 7<br>They are all gone. I saw Leto in Despise with the Trolls. The others too have joined creatures of their type. The gypsies will not speak to me. They have finally realized that whatever I'm doing",
	[1114001] = L"is bad. It wasn't meant to be! I couldn't bear to face Lydia. This is my last attempt. This must work or all is lot. If it fails, I hope my beloved wife will forgive me.",
	[1114002] = L"DAY 8<br>Sthytys asara... Shaslishyth. Iss. ",
	[1114003] = L"Recommend Shard",
	[1114004] = L"gazer halloween costume",
	[1114005] = L"a murky mixture",
	[1114006] = L"bloodworm halloween costume",
	[1114007] = L"Tiny glares at you menacingly. You will need to show him proof you are invited in. ",
	[1114008] = L"dream wraith halloween costume",
	[1114009] = L"shadow wyrm halloween costume",
	[1114010] = L"Tiny mumbles in acceptance of the note and seems to lose interest in you.",
	[1114011] = L"Amateurs!! That's what happens when you mess with things you don't understand. Yes, I can Cure that.",
	[1114012] = L"If you want my help, you must first bring me a sample of what's ailing the patient.",
	[1114013] = L"Magical Herbs",
	[1114014] = L"moon grass",
	[1114015] = L"MOON GRASS<br>Of all seasonal plants, it is one of the most powerful. It grows around graveyards for a few days around Hallows Eve. When used on the corpse of a monster, one has a chance of",
	[1114016] = L"harvesting corporeal residue. The stronger the creature it was harvested from, the more potent the residue will be. Four grams of residue suffice to make a corporeal essence. Those are a wonder as",
	[1114017] = L"well. If you apply the essence on yourself you will temporarily be morphed into a random creature, based on the potency of the residue used to make your essence. The effects are amazing. ",
	[1114018] = L"You can see things you couldn't perceive as a human, other creatures also leave you be, thinking you're one of them. But beware!! If you sustain damage or attack any other creature, the effects will",
	[1114019] = L"wear off! Just like moon grass, the corporeal essence can only be used so many times before it's used up so use it wisely!<br><br>So why do all this? For the Lingering Souls ",
	[1114020] = L"of course! As a monster if you roam in dungeons, you will run into red lights flickering. It is the lingering souls of the dead. Capture them with a soul harvester. Once full, use the flask at an alchemy table",
	[1114021] = L"to turn it into crystallized essence. It will turn into one of three things:<br><br>BLUE CRYSTAL<br>Cures any disease or ailment. Very effective against morphing.",
	[1114022] = L"RED CRYSTAL<br>Used to make stable monster costumes.<br><br>GOLD CRYSTAL<br>Used to summon a Harbinger. Not for the faint of heart!",
	[1114023] = L"You collect a sprig of moon grass and put it in your backpack.",
	[1114024] = L"Select the alchemy table you want to process this on.",
	[1114025] = L"You haven't harvested enough souls to do this yet.",
	[1114026] = L"Your recommended shard is:",
	[1114027] = L"There are no resources left. Try again in a few minutes.",
	[1114028] = L"You harvest the last resources from this plant.",
	[1114029] = L"Select the corpse you wish to use this on.",
	[1114030] = L"You gather the residue and place it in your backpack.",
	[1114031] = L"This creature has already been drained.",
	[1114032] = L"corporeal residue",
	[1114033] = L"Help me pick a shard!",
	[1114034] = L"Please note this down somewhere so that you do not forget.",
	[1114035] = L"crystallized essence",
	[1114036] = L"This looks like a very potent cure for a rare illness.",
	[1114037] = L"Oh my!! I've seen this before! Beware if you use it. It summons a fiendish creature!",
	[1114038] = L"You have turned in ~1_COUNT~ red crystallized essence. Turn in ~2_NUM~ more to get a reward.",
	[1114039] = L"Thank you!! For every 5 red crystallized essences you bring me, I shall give you another reward!",
	[1114040] = L"Administer it to Jared or one of his helpers. It should slowly help restore them to their old self.",
	[1114041] = L"This will summon a formidable creature. Make sure to have friends with you when you do!",
	[1114042] = L"Bring this to Tomas. He can use it. That's what Jared was trying to accomplish.",
	[1114043] = L"The Toymaker might have a use for this.",
	[1114044] = L"You apply the cure and your patient seems a little better.",
	[1114045] = L"My savior!! I never thought I would be back to my old self again!! I'm eternally in your debt!",
	[1114046] = L"Thank you, but I'm fully recovered now. Maybe another of my comrades could use it.",
