	[1060399] = L"<a href=\"?ForceTopic45\">Karma</a> is closely related to the effectiveness of Paladin abilities.  In short, the higher your level of <a href=\"?ForceTopic45\">Karma</a> is, the more effective your Paladin abilities will be.  Lower <a href=\"?ForceTopic45\">Karma</a>, on the other hand, will decrease the effectiveness of your Paladin abilities.<BR><BR>A Paladin should always strive to follow the virtues, thus naturally increasing his <a href=\"?ForceTopic45\">Karma</a> and making him the most powerful Paladin he can be.",
