	[1061491] = L"Heals the target of damage.  The caster\x2019s Karma affects the amount of damage healed.",
	[1061492] = L"Temporarily enchants the weapon the caster is currently wielding.  The type of damage the weapon inflicts when hitting a target will be converted to the target\x2019s worst Resistance type. Duration of the effect is affected by the caster\x2019s Karma.",
	[1061493] = L"Attempts to dispel evil summoned creatures and cause other evil creatures to flee from combat.  Transformed Necromancers may also take Stamina and Mana Damage.  Caster\x2019s Karma and Chivalry, and Target\x2019s Fame or Necromancy affect Dispel chance.",
