	[1061497] = L"Attempts to Resurrect, Cure, and Heal all targets in a radius around the caster. If any target is successfully assisted, the Paladin\x2019s current Hit Points, Mana, and Stamina are greatly reduced.  Amount of damage healed is affected by the Caster\x2019s Karma.",
	[1061498] = L"Attempts to remove all Curse effects from Target. Curses include Mage spells such as Clumsy, Weaken, Feeblemind, and Paralyze, as well as all Necromancer curses. Chance of removing curse is affected by the Caster\x2019s Karma.",
