	[1078014] = L"You have proven yourself young one. You will continue to improve as your skills are honed with age. You are an honorable warrior, worthy of the rank of Apprentice Samurai.  Please accept this no-dachi as a gift. It is called \"The Dragon's Tail\". Upon a successful strike in combat, there is a chance this mighty weapon will replenish your stamina equal to the damage of your attack. I hope \"The Dragon's Tail\" serves you well. You have earned it. Farewell for now.",
