	[1078100] = L"Bushido is the main skill of the Samurai, and embodies the very essence of honorable combat. With it, and the Book of Bushido, the Samurai can perform a variety of special abilities that are defensive in nature, but can be used to quickly and honorably defeat the toughest of opponents.",
