	[1078122] = L"Wanna learn how to make powerful weapons and armor? Talk to me.",
	[1154296] = L"I\x2019m looking to expand my operation here, before I can do that though I need a more reliable source of raw ore.  Rumor has it the Orcs have a new machine they are using to drill huge quantities of ore!",
	[1023391] = L"brambles",
	[1078124] = L"You there! I can use some help mining these rocks!",
	[1023392] = L"brambles",
	[1078126] = L"Meditation allows a mage to replenish mana quickly. I can teach you.",
	[1023393] = L"tree",
	[1078128] = L"You there! Wanna master hand to hand defense? Of course you do!",
	[1023394] = L"tree",
	[1154292] = L"You've got one! I don't know how but you did!  This will prove invaluable in my research! I will do as promised.  Long ago I learned of a set of items known as the Salvager's Suit.  It had been quite some time since anyone had seen the actual plans - or a suit for that matter, but legend tells any who wear the suit will be aided in undersea exploration.  Last anyone heard the plans could be found deep within the Sorcerer's Dungeon in Ilshenar.",
	[1023395] = L"tree",
	[1078130] = L"A mage should learn how to resist spells.",
	[1023396] = L"tree",
