	[1023397] = L"leaves",
	[1078134] = L"Seek me to learn the way of the samurai.",
	[1023398] = L"leaves",
	[1154288] = L"Hepler sent me to ask about Shipwrecks...",
	[1023399] = L"leaves",
	[1078136] = L"There is an art to slaying your enemies swiftly. It's called tactics, and I can teach it to you.",
	[1023400] = L"leaves",
	[1078138] = L"Learning of the body will allow you to excel in combat.",
	[1023401] = L"leaves",
	[1078140] = L"Want to learn how to parry blows?",
	[1023402] = L"leaves",
	[1154284] = L"Well well! Lookie here! That's a fine pull indeed!  Shame we can only salvage with hooks and the like...if only we could peak beneath the waves and score the big hauls! Say, I heard once of a Master Tinker that may be able to tell of a suit specially made for exploring deep ship wrecks...if you manage to get your hands on one of those suits return to me and I'll share a map with you showing the location of a secret wreck only I know about!",
