	[1078222] = L"Walker's Leggings",
	[1023473] = L"vines",
	[1078224] = L"You\x2019ll notice a little marker on the map. That\x2019s a waypoint.<br><br>This waypoint shows you where a gate is. Follow the alley towards the marker, and head through the gate.<br><br>To open the gate, or any other door for that matter, just Double Left Click on it and it will open.",
	[1023474] = L"vines",
	[1154212] = L"You may not use the Purge Magic spell while you are under its curse.",
	[1023475] = L"vines",
	[1078226] = L"Great, now you are in an aggressive stance, perfect for fighting. <br><br>That\x2019s hot.<br><br>Now remember to toggle back into Peace mode before you try to interact with friendly townsfolk.<br><br>They don\x2019t usually take kindly to being attacked.<br><br>Now, select a target by left clicking on a skeleton.",
	[1023476] = L"apple tree",
	[1078228] = L"You destroyed one! <br><br>Nice work! <br><br>Now you can check it to see if it was carrying anything of value.<br><br>To do this, double left click on the corpse. ",
	[1023477] = L"leaves",
	[1078230] = L"Well Done. <br><br>Now when you are hurt, or have taken any damage, it\x2019s a good idea to heal up before going into battle again. <br><br>You have a Potion of Healing, which you found on the corpse, in your inventory.<br><br>To use the potion: Double Left Click on it in your inventory and you will drink it.",
