	[1094978] = L"Travel into the Abyss and seek three samples of fertile dirt and three samples of bone.  Bring them to Gretchen for your reward.<br><center>-----</center><br>This place in dreams has called to me, it is to magic as a tree.  Passages stretch like limbs laden fair with a bounty of fruit in the form of a... err... reagents.<br><br>Ahem... Not that I would see you hurt, but the first thing I need is some Fertile Dirt.   Second I will need some bone, long forgotten, far from home.  Return to me with three of each, a special potion will I share with you this one time.",
