	[1152461] = L"This property indicates that a percentage of the damage inflicted by the weapon (or spell) will be physical damage.  Physical damage is applied against an opponent\x2019s physical resistance.",
	[1025105] = L"ringmail leggings",
	[1152460] = L"This property provides a chance for a burst of mana restoring magic to affect the player when the player is taking damage.  The amount of mana restored is based on the player\x2019s maximum mana and the player\x2019s current karma level.  Each piece of karma mana burst equipment that the user is wearing will increases the frequency of the mana restoring bursts.  There are both positive and negative karma versions of these items.",
	[1025106] = L"ringmail gloves",
	[1152459] = L"This property provides a reduction in the amount of arrows or bolts an archer uses.  The reduction is based on a random chance that an arrow or bolt shot from a weapon will not be consumed.",
	[1021669] = L"barred metal door",
	[1152457] = L"This property provides a cumulative percentage bonus that increases the effectiveness of any fishing bait that is used by the wearer.",
	[1025108] = L"crook",
	[1152456] = L"This property indicates that an item has been crafted by a crafter of exceptional skill.  Exceptionally crafted items can carry their maker\x2019s mark and also provide various additional bonuses depending on whether they are armor or weapons.  The bonuses include increased basic resistances for armor, increased damage increase for weapons and increased imbuing potential for both weapons and armor.  Some of these bonuses can be further increased by a crafter\x2019s arms lore skill.",
	[1025109] = L"crook",
