	[1027861] = L"unfinished barrel",
	[1072683] = L"~1_NAME~ has already activated the Prism, please wait...",
	[1027862] = L"empty tool kit",
	[1072685] = L"The ratmen have holes all over the place that lead to their warrens.  Sometimes they're loitering around on the surface too.  Either way, they're not hard to find.",
	[1027863] = L"empty tool kit",
	[1072687] = L"I quite understand your reluctance.  If you reconsider, I'll be here.",
	[1027864] = L"tool kit",
	[1072689] = L"Cowards!",
	[1027865] = L"tool kit",
	[1072691] = L"Bearing Gifts",
	[1027866] = L"tool kit",
	[1072693] = L"The Brawn",
	[1027867] = L"tool kit",
	[1072695] = L"The unbless failed.",
	[1027868] = L"tinker's tools",
	[1072697] = L"When you were exterminating those untidy vermin, you must have noticed the archers amongst them?  Those cowardly rats have been peppering us with arrows and then running away before we can retaliate.  Can I count on you to handle this for me?",
	[1027869] = L"wheat sheaf",
	[1072699] = L"Please, I beg of you, reconsider!",
	[1027870] = L"wheat sprouts",
	[1072701] = L"Ah my friend, thank you again for your timely aid!  The ring is finally complete and I'm ready to reveal to Ciala my love for her.  Would you ... could you present her with my token?",
	[1027871] = L"wheat sprouts",
	[1072703] = L"arcane circle",
	[1027872] = L"pickpocket dip",
	[1072705] = L"You must be standing on an arcane circle, pentagram or abbatoir to use this spell.",
	[1027873] = L"pickpocket dip",
	[1072707] = L"*sigh*  We have so much to do to clean this area up.  Even the fine work you did on those ogres didn't have much of an impact on the community.  It's the ogre lords that direct the actions of the other ogres, let's strike at the leaders and perhaps that will thwart the miserable curs.",
	[1027874] = L"pickpocket dip",
	[1072709] = L"Ogre Lords are pretty easy to recognize.  They're the ones ordering the other ogres about in a lordly manner.  Striking down their leadership will throw the ogres into confusion and dismay!",
	[1027875] = L"pickpocket dip",
	[1072711] = L"Oh, I see.  *sigh*  Perhaps I overestimated your abilities.",
	[1027876] = L"pickpocket dip",
	[1072713] = L"The ogre insurgency has taken a turn for the worse!  I've just been advised that the titans have concluded their discussions with the ogres and they've allied.  We have virtually no information about titans.  Engage them and appraise their mettle.",
	[1027877] = L"pickpocket dip",
	[1072715] = L"Those titans don't skulk very well.  You should be able to track them easily ... their footsteps are easily the largest around.",
	[1027878] = L"dropping coins",
	[1072717] = L"Bureaucratic Delay",
	[1027879] = L"dropping coins",
	[1072719] = L"Special Delivery",
	[1027880] = L"dropping coins",
	[1072721] = L"Hrmph!",
	[1027881] = L"dropping coins",
	[1072723] = L"Access to the Stacks",
	[1027882] = L"pylon",
	[1072725] = L"I do apologize for being unprepared. Perhaps when you return later I'll have more wax in stock.",
	[1027883] = L"pylon",
	[1072727] = L"What's this?  Sealing wax ... Sarakki ... official documents ... Oh, I see.  Can do, can do.  You will need to get me the poison sacs of course.  They are so volatile they aren't viable after an hour or so ... yes, yes.  Right, well off you go, speckled scorpions are the only critters that have the right poison.  They live in the desert near here.",
	[1027884] = L"pylon",
	[1072729] = L"Hello, hello!  Speckled, that's what they are.  All covered with spots and speckles when you look very closely.  Speckled scorpion poison sacs will do the trick.",
	[1027885] = L"light",
	[1072731] = L"Your foot brushes against a wire, tripping a hidden trap!",
	[1027886] = L"light",
	[1072733] = L"The air suddenly stirs around you. From the darkness you feel the sting of the Serpent's Fang!",
	[1027887] = L"light",
	[1072735] = L"From the dark corners spring the Claw of the Tiger.",
	[1027888] = L"light",
	[1072737] = L"The sickening crunch under your feet alerts you of another trap filled with murderous fiends.",
	[1027889] = L"light",
	[1072739] = L"You hear a click behind the wall.",
	[1027890] = L"light",
	[1072741] = L"Good good!  The wax is just cooling now and will be ready by the time you get it back to Sarakki.  You still want the wax, right?",
	[1027891] = L"target",
	[1072743] = L"Sealing Wax Order",
	[1027892] = L"target",
	[1072745] = L"Notarized Application.",
	[1027893] = L"target",
	[1072747] = L"Hello, hello.  No rush of course.  I'm sure Sarakki is patient and doesn't mind waiting for the wax.",
