	[1072759] = L"The Way of the Arcanist",
	[1027900] = L"magical door",
	[1072761] = L"Learning to weave spells and control the forces of nature requires sacrifice, discipline, focus, and an unwavering dedication to Sosaria herself.  We do not teach the unworthy.  They do not comprehend the lessons nor the dedication required.  If you would walk the path of the Arcanist, then you must do as I require without hesitation or question.  Your first task is to rid our home of rats ... 50 of them in the next hour.",
	[1027901] = L"magical door",
	[1072763] = L"The way of the Arcanist involves cooperation with others and a strong committment to the community of your people.  We have run low on the cotton we use to pack wounds and our people have need.  Bring 10 bales of cotton to me.",
	[1027902] = L"magical door",
	[1072765] = L"With health and defense assured, we need look to the need of the community for food and drink.  We will feast on fish steaks, sweets, and wine.  You will supply the ingredients, the cooks will prepare the meal.  As a Arcanist relies upon others to build focus and lend their power to her workings, the community needs the effort of all to survive.",
	[1027903] = L"magical door",
	[1072767] = L"*nods* Not everyone has the temperment to undertake the way of the Arcanist.",
	[1027904] = L"magical door",
	[1072769] = L"The people have need of these items.  You are proving yourself inadequate to the demands of a member of this community.",
	[1072770] = L"Do not falter now.  You have begun to show promise.",
	[1072771] = L"You must serve Sosaria with all your heart and strength.  Your unwillingness does not reflect favorably upon you.",
	[1027906] = L"magical door",
	[1072773] = L"You waste my time.  The task is simple. Kill 50 rats in an hour.",
	[1027907] = L"magical door",
	[1072775] = L"I care not where you acquire the cotton, merely that you provide it.",
	[1027908] = L"magical door",
	[1072777] = L"Where are the items you've been tasked to supply for the feast?",
