	[1072961] = L"Contraband",
	[1028001] = L"Telekinesis",
	[1072963] = L"I have a task for you ... adventurer.  Will you risk all to win great renown?  The Black Order is organized into three sects, each with their own speciality.  The Dragon's Flame serves the will of the Grand Mage, the Tiger's Claw answers to the Master Thief, and the Serpent's Fang kills at the direction of the High Executioner.  Slay all three and you will strike the order a devastating blow!",
	[1028002] = L"Teleport",
	[1072965] = L"You have discovered a bundle of stolen property.  Will you return it to its rightful owner?",
	[1028003] = L"Unlock",
	[1072967] = L"I wish to make a statement of censure against the elite ninjas of the Black Order.  Deliver, in the strongest manner, my disdain.  But do not make war on women, even those that take arms against you.  It is not ... fitting.",
	[1028004] = L"Wall of Stone",
	[1072969] = L"The Serpent's Fang sect members have gone too far!  Express to them my displeasure by slaying ten of them.  But remember, I do not condone war on women, so I will only accept the deaths of men, human and elf.",
	[1028005] = L"Arch Cure",
	[1072971] = L"*whisper* It's a very dangerous task.  Let me know if you change your mind.",
	[1028006] = L"Arch Protection",
	[1072973] = L"I do not fault your decision.",
	[1028007] = L"Curse",
	[1072975] = L"Many fear to tangle with the wicked sorceress.  I understand and appreciate your concerns.",
	[1028008] = L"Fire Field",
	[1072977] = L"Of course, you could also choose to keep the bundle.",
	[1028009] = L"Greater Heal",
	[1072979] = L"As you wish.",
	[1028010] = L"Lightning",
	[1072981] = L"Or perhaps you'd rather not.",
