	[1072997] = L"Blood Suckers",
	[1028019] = L"Poison Field",
	[1072999] = L"Specimens",
	[1028020] = L"Summon Creature",
	[1073001] = L"Voracious Plants",
	[1028021] = L"Dispel",
	[1073003] = L"Mongbat Menace!",
	[1028022] = L"Energy Bolt",
	[1073005] = L"Dead Drones",
	[1028023] = L"Explosion",
	[1073007] = L"Birds of a Feather",
	[1028024] = L"Invisibility",
	[1073009] = L"Why?  I ask you why?  They walk around after they're put in the ground.  It's just wrong in so many ways.  Put them to proper rest, I beg you.  I'll find some way to pay you for the kindness. Just kill five zombies and five skeletons.",
	[1028025] = L"Mark",
	[1073011] = L"Why?  I ask you why?  They walk around after they're put in the ground.  It's just wrong in so many ways.  Put them to proper rest, I beg you.  I'll find some way to pay you for the kindness. Just kill eight patchwork skeletons.",
	[1028026] = L"Mass Curse",
	[1073013] = L"You can't trust them, you know.  Lizardmen I mean.  They have forked tongues ... and you know what that means.  Exterminate ten of them and I'll reward you.",
	[1028027] = L"Paralyze Field",
	[1073015] = L"Those green-skinned freaks have run off with more of my livestock.  I want an orc scout killed for each sheep I lost and an orc for each chicken.  So that's four orc scouts and eight orcs I'll pay you to slay.",
	[1028028] = L"Reveal",
	[1073017] = L"It's a big job but you look to be just the adventurer to do it!  I'm so glad you came by ... I'm paying well for the death of five ogres and five ettins.  Hop to it, if you're so inclined.",
	[1028029] = L"Chain Lightning",
	[1073019] = L"Hahahaha!  I knew it!",
	[1028030] = L"Energy Field",
	[1073021] = L"I bet you can't kill ... ten gore fiends!  I bet they're too much for you.  You may as well confess you can't ... <br>",
	[1028031] = L"Flamestrike",
	[1073023] = L"I bet you can't kill ... ten gibberlings!  I bet they're too much for you.  You may as well confess you can't ... ",
	[1028032] = L"Gate Travel",
	[1073025] = L"I bet you can't tangle with those bloodsuckers ... say around ten vampire bats!  I bet they're too much for you.  You may as well confess you can't ... ",
	[1028033] = L"Mana Vampire",
	[1073027] = L"It's a big job but you look to be just the adventurer to do it!  I'm so glad you came by ... I'm paying well for the death of six giant ice serpents and six frost spiders.  Hop to it, if you're so inclined.<br>",
	[1028034] = L"Mass Dispel",
	[1073029] = L"You've got to help me out! Those ratmen have been causing absolute havok around here.  Kill them off before they destroy my land.  I'll pay you if you kill off twelve of those dirty rats.<br>",
	[1028035] = L"Meteor Swarm",
	[1073031] = L"Have you ever seen what a slime can do to good gear?  Well, it's not pretty, let me tell you!  If you take on my task to destroy twelve of them, bear that in mind.  They'll corrode your equipment faster than anything.",
	[1028036] = L"Polymorph",
	[1073033] = L"I imagine you don't know about the mongbats.  Well, you may think you do, but I know more than just about anyone.  You see they come in two varieties ... the stronger and the weaker.  Either way, they're a menace.  Exterminate ten of the weaker ones and four of the stronger and I'll pay you an honest wage.",
