	[1112523] = L"A pleasure to have met you. I hope for your safe return in these dark times.",
	[1150277] = L"Transfer Merchant Inventory to Stables",
	[1073555] = L"You skin it and place the cut-up hides in your backpack.",
	[1073556] = L"R.I.P. Lady Malynn",
	[1073557] = L"Here lies Kothar",
	[1073558] = L"Farewell Ibn Shaun",
	[1073559] = L"You attempt to recover ~1_NUM~ ~2_AMMO~, but there is no room in your backpack, and they are lost.",
	[1073560] = L"In memory of Mordanna",
	[1073561] = L"Can you hear them? The never-ending howling? The incessant wailing? These banshees, they never cease! Never! They haunt my nights. Please, I beg you -- will you silence them? I would be ever so grateful. ",
	[1073562] = L"Some say killing a boggling brings good luck. I don't place much stock in old wives' tales, but I can say a few dead bogglings would certainly be lucky for me! Help me out and I can reward you for your efforts. ",
	[1073563] = L"Nobody told me about the Mummy's Curse. How was I supposed to know you shouldn't disturb the tombs? Oh, sure, now all I hear about is the curse of the vengeful dead. I'll tell you what -- make a few of these mummies go away and we'll keep this between you and me.",
	[1073564] = L"You want to hear about trouble? I got trouble. How's angry piles of granite walking around for trouble? Maybe they don't like the mining, maybe it's the farming. I don't know. All I know is someone's got to turn them back to potting soil. And it'd be worth a pretty penny to the soul that does it.",
	[1073565] = L"Please, hear me kind traveler. You know when a knight falls, sometimes they are cursed to roam the earth as undead mockeries of their former glory? That is too grim a fate for even any knight to suffer! Please, put them out of their misery. I will offer you what payment I can if you will end the torment of these undead wretches. ",
	[1073566] = L"It is a piteous thing when the dead continue to walk the earth. Restless spirits are known to inhabit these parts, taking the lives of unwary travelers. It is about time a hero put the dead back in their graves. I'm sure such a hero would be justly rewarded.",
	[1073567] = L"Imps! Do you hear me? Imps! They're everywhere! They're in everything! Oh, don't be fooled by their size -- they vicious little devils! Half-sized evil incarnate, they are! Somebody needs to send them back to where they came from, if you know what I mean. ",
	[1073568] = L"The Terathan are an aggressive species. Left unchecked, they will swarm across our lands. And where will that leave us? Compost in the hive, that's what! Stop them, stop them cold my friend. Kill their warriors and you'll check their movement, that is certain.",
	[1073569] = L"I've seen them hiding in their webs among the woods. Glassy eyes, spindly legs, poisonous fangs. Monsters, I say! Deadly horrors, these black widows. Someone must exterminate the abominations! If only I could find a worthy hero for such a task, then I could give them this considerable reward.",
	[1073570] = L"Why must the dead plague the living? With their foul necromancy and dark sorceries, the undead menace the countryside. I fear what will happen if no one is strong enough to face these nightmare sorcerers and thin their numbers.",
	[1073571] = L"Foul brutes! No one loves an orc, but some of them are worse than the rest. Their Captains and their Bombers, for instance, they're the worst of the lot. Kill a few of those, and the rest are just a rabble. Exterminate a few of them and you'll make the world a sunnier place, don't you know. ",
	[1073572] = L"Thank goodness, a hero like you has arrived! Brigands have descended upon this area like locusts, stealing and looting where ever they go. We need someone to put these vile curs where they belong -- in their graves. Are you up to the task? ",
	[1073573] = L"A Solen hive is a fascinating piece of ecology. It's put together like a finely crafted clock. Who knows what happens if you remove something? So let's find out. Exterminate a few of the warriors and I'll make it worth your while.",
	[1073574] = L"Kind traveler, hear my plea. You know of the evil orbs? The wrathful eyes? Some call them gazers? They must be a nest nearby, for they are tormenting us poor folk. We need to drive back their numbers. But we are not strong enough to face such horrors ourselves, we need a true hero. ",
	[1073575] = L"Vermin! They get into everything! I told the boy to leave out some poisoned cheese -- and they shot him. What else can I do? Unless\x2026these ratmen are skilled with a bow, but I'd lay a wager you're better, eh? Could you skin a few of the wretches for me?",
	[1073576] = L"The woods in these parts are restless. Wrathful trees, walking about. Why, they're a menace to decent folk! And I'm running low on firewood, so what do you say? Could you turn a few reapers into some useful lumber?",
	[1073577] = L"Were you the sort of child that enjoyed knocking over anthills? Well, perhaps you'd like to try something a little bigger? There's a Solen nest nearby and I bet if you killed a queen or two, it would be quite the sight to behold.  I'd even pay to see that -- what do you say? ",
	[1073578] = L"It makes no sense! Cold blooded serpents cannot live in the ice! It's a biological impossibility! They are an abomination against reason! Please, I beg you -- kill them! Make them disappear for me! Do this and I will reward you. ",
	[1073579] = L"The universe is all about balance my friend. Tip one end, you must balance the other. That's why I must ask you to kill not just one kind of elemental, but three kinds. Snuff out some Fire, douse a few Water, and crush some Earth elementals and I'll pay you for your trouble.",
	[1073580] = L"I hope you'll reconsider. Until then, farwell.",
	[1073581] = L"Until you kill 12 Wailing Banshees, there will be no peace. ",
	[1073582] = L"Go back and kill all 20 bogglings!",
	[1073583] = L"Uh, I don't think you're quite done killing Mummies yet. <br>",
	[1073584] = L"You got rocks in your head? I said to kill 12 earth elementals, okay?<br>",
	[1073585] = L"Your task is not done. Continue putting the Skeleton and Bone Knights to rest.<br>",
	[1073586] = L"The restless spirts still walk -- you must kill 15 of them.",
	[1073587] = L"Don't let the little devils scare you! You  kill 12 imps -- then we'll talk reward.<br>",
	[1073588] = L"Unless you kill at least 10 Terathan Warriors, you won't have any impact on their hive.<br>",
	[1073589] = L"You've got a good start, but to stop the black-eyed fiends, you need to kill a dozen. <br>",
	[1073590] = L"Surely, a brave soul like yourself can kill 10 Bone Magi and Skeletal Mages?<br>",
	[1073591] = L"The only good orc is a dead orc -- and 4 dead Captains and 6 dead Bombers is even better!<br>",
	[1073592] = L"The Brigands still plague us. Have you killed 20 of their number?<br>",
	[1073593] = L"I don't think you've gotten their attention yet -- you need to kill at least 10 Solen Warriors.<br>",
	[1073594] = L"Have you annihilated a dozen Gazers yet, kind traveler?<br>",
	[1073595] = L"I don't see 10 tails from Ratman Archers on your belt -- and until I do, no reward for you.<br>",
	[1073596] = L"I'm thinking of building a small shed and the lumber of 15 reapers would be just about right.<br>",
	[1073597] = L"Dead Solen Queens isn't too much to ask, is it?",
	[1073598] = L"You wouldn't try and just pretend you murdered 10 Giant Ice Worms, would you?<br>",
	[1073599] = L"Four of each, that's all I ask. Water, earth and fire. <br>",
	[1073600] = L"Your quest is complete. Return for your reward.",
	[1073601] = L"Finally, some peace and quiet! You've more than earned this reward.",
	[1073602] = L"Well, I don't feel any luckier, but there's sure a lot less bogglings about. Good job, my friend.<br>",
	[1073603] = L"Nice work. Now, here's something for your trouble -- and this will stay between you and me, right?<br>",
	[1073604] = L"Well, you're turned them rocky horrors into gravel, didn't you? You've got my thanks -- and this reward.<br>",
	[1073605] = L"You've done a noble deed, putting these undead down. I only wish I could give you a greater reward than this.<br>",
	[1073606] = L"The spirits are now at peace. Please, take this as a reward for your work.<br>",
	[1073607] = L"Oh, I hope those little buggers are burning where you sent 'em! Here's a little something to fill out your purse.<br>",
	[1073608] = L"My friend, take this reward for your work in driving back the Terathan hive.<br>",
	[1073609] = L"I haven't seen a single web since you cleared the area. You've more than earned this.<br>",
	[1073610] = L"Pleace accept this modest offer for your bravery in facing those undead sorcerers.<br>",
	[1073611] = L"Mmm. Smells like dead orc, out there! Nicely turned! Fatten your purse with this, then!<br>",
	[1073612] = L"You've brought a measure of peace to this area. Please, accept this meager offering as reward.<br>",
	[1073613] = L"It's fascinating to watch the nest in action, isn't it? Here's something for your trouble.<br>",
	[1073614] = L"I no longer feel their prying gaze of evil upon me. For that, I give thanks to you -- here's is your reward.<br>",
	[1073615] = L"Hmm, looks like you've built the better rat-trap. Enjoy a little reward then!<br>",
	[1073616] = L"Yes, I like these woods much better without the trees wandering about. Nice job. <br>",
	[1073617] = L"Did you seem them run around? Wasn't that great? Here, take this reward -- that\x2019s the most fun I've had in days.<br>",
	[1073618] = L"I think Giant Ice Worms are a myth, don't you? Shh, I don't want to talk about it -- just take the money and be gone.",
	[1073619] = L"You've restored the natural balance friend and earned this generous reward.<br>",
	[1073620] = L"You have not learned this recipe.",
	[1073621] = L"Your reward has been placed in your backpack.",
