	[1073674] = L"Frosty Welcome",
	[1073675] = L"Back to the Pit",
	[1073676] = L"Brutal Measures",
	[1073677] = L"The All Seeing Eye",
	[1073678] = L"Mother's Day Surprise",
	[1073679] = L"The Shoulders of Giants<br>",
	[1073680] = L"Orc Bane",
	[1073681] = L"Burning Desire",
	[1073682] = L"Albino Atrocity",
	[1073683] = L"Toxic Avengers",
	[1073684] = L"Hero's Journey",
	[1073685] = L"How Do They Pronounce That?",
	[1073686] = L"Temptation",
	[1073687] = L"Destroying the Destroyers",
	[1073688] = L"Masters of the Underworld",
	[1073689] = L"Evil Rears It's Undead Head",
	[1073690] = L"Xenophobia",
	[1073691] = L"An Unsavory Task",
	[1073692] = L"Better to Be Old and Mean",
	[1073693] = L"Riddle Me This",
	[1073694] = L"I must implore you, brave traveler, to do battle with the vile reptiles which haunt these parts. Those hideous abominations, the Ophidians, are a blight across the land. If you were able to put down a host of the scaly warriors, the Knights or the Avengers, I would forever be in your debt.",
	[1073695] = L"There's been a bumper crop of evil with the Bog Things in these parts, my friend. Though they are foul creatures, they are also most fecund. Slay one and you make the land more fertile. Even better, slay several and I will give you whatever coin I can spare. ",
	[1073696] = L"Psst. Listen close my friend, for I'll not speak of this again. Unicorns. You know them, I know them. I need a number of them gone. Don't ask why something you beautiful needs to be destroyed. If you can manage the task, I have the means to reward you handsomely. ",
	[1073697] = L"It is regretable that the Gargoyles insist upon warring with us. Their Enforcers attack men on sight, despite all efforts at reason. To help maintain order in this region, I have been authorized to encourage bounty hunters to reduce their numbers. Eradicate their number and I will reward you handsomely.",
	[1073698] = L"You think you've seen destruction and horror, my friend? You haven't seen anything until you've seen what a Giant Beetle can do to a nicely tilled garden. There's been a swarm of 'em lately. I don't have much, but if you could rid the area of a few, I'm sure I could find something to reward you with.",
	[1073699] = L"If I had but one wish, it would be to rid myself of these dread Efreet! Fire and ash, they are cunning and deadly! You look a brave soul --would you be interested in earning a rich reward for slaughtering a few of the smoky devils?",
	[1073700] = L"Is there anything more foul than a pixie? They have cruel eyes and a mind for mischief, I say. I don't care if some think they're cute -- I say kill them and let the Avatar sort them out. In fact, if you were to kill a few pixies, I'd make sure you had a few coins to rub together, if you get my meaning.",
	[1073701] = L"They aren't called Dread Spiders because they're fluffy and cuddly now, are they? No, there's nothing appealing about those wretches so I sure wouldn't lose any sleep if you were to exterminate a few. I'd even part with a generous amount of gold, I would.",
	[1073702] = L"Feel that chill in the air? It means an icy death for the unwary, for deadly Ice Elementals are about. Who knows what magic summoned them, what's important now is getting rid of them. I don't have much, but I'll give all I can if you'd only stop the cold-hearted monsters.",
	[1073703] = L"I should be trimming back the vegetation here, but something nasty has taken root. Vicious vines I can't go near. If there's any hope of getting things under control, some one's going to need to destroy a few of those Whipping Vines. Someone strong and fast and tough. ",
	[1073704] = L"Ants are industrious and Lions are noble so who'd think an Ant Lion would be such a problem? The Ant Lions have been causing mindless destruction in these parts. I suppose it's just how ants are. But I need you to help eliminate the infestation. Would you be willing to help for a bit of reward?<br>",
	[1073705] = L"They're unholy, I say. Golems, a walking mockery of all life, born of blackest magic. They're not truly alive, so destroying them isn't a crime, it's a service. A service I will gladly pay for.",
	[1073706] = L"It baffles me how a Ratman can be smart enough to learn magic. But, I don't think they're so smart you couldn't kill a few. The beady-eyed fiends have been causing trouble in these parts, so I'd be glad to reward someone who thinned their numbers.",
	[1073707] = L"The flap of their leathery wings, the scratch of their reptillian claws, the clank of their scales. Keep your eyes open, friend for there are Drakes in these parts. The unwary find themselves a hot meal for the cold blooded fiends. I'd give all the treasure I possess to anyone brave enough to scourge a number of those devils from our fair skies.",
	[1073708] = L"From the foul depths, the Kraken come to torment men. The scaly horrors make life near impossible for us all. I know it may not be much, but I'd gladly reward any who were fearless enough to face the Kraken and reduce their host!",
	[1073709] = L"I have a business proposition for you, my friend. Caravans would like to move freely across our fair deserts except the accursed Sand Vortexes always attack them. If you could, say \"disenchant\" a few Vortexes, I could compensate you for your efforts in encouraging free trade. ",
	[1073710] = L"These demon horses mock the bond between rider and steed! It pains me to see such despicable monsters in the shape of a noble horse. Please, execute these unholy mockeries, the Nightmares or the Fire Steeds, for me -- do this, and I will gladly reward you.",
	[1073711] = L"You've heard of a snake in the grass? How about a serpent in a lava field? Those fiery monsters cause no end of trouble, slithering and burning. Find a way to turn a few lava serpents into charcoal and I'll make sure you leave with a heavy purse.",
	[1073712] = L"Those frosty brutes! It's impossible to make a decent bonfire with them about! I'm talking about those masters of ice magic, the Arctic Ogre Lords. Yes, I'd certainly add a few coins to the purse of anyone tough enough to turn a few of those brutes into ice cubes!",
	[1073713] = L"Devils of snow and ice! They steal the warmth from our very souls! If only someone were brave enough to face the dread Ice Fiends and reduce their numbers, then decent folk might have a chance for once!",
	[1073714] = L"From the Stygian depths, the Daemons rise to torment poor humankind! I've seen them, cutting a swath of destruction through our fair land. But you, you seem a hardy adventurous sort. Perhaps you have experience in slaying foul daemons?",
	[1073715] = L"Corpulent foul-smelling brutes! Without their leaders, your average ogre is such a menace. But as long as the Ogre Lords are around, they whip that unsightly rabble into shape. Hmm, makes you think we should target a few of these Orge Lords, doesn't it?",
	[1073716] = L"They watching me! Shh! They might hear! They've had their eyes on me for a while -- no, I'm not paranoid! Have you seen the way they look at me? Elder Gazers, indeed! Why do they observe me so? Please, kind traveler -- kill the fiends! Close their never-blinking eyes once and for all and I will gladly reward you!",
	[1073717] = L"My dear old mum, she does hate those awful Terathan. She'd like nothing better than to wreck their hives. Hmm, you know -- kill a Terathan Matriarch and the hive drops in efficiency. I wonder\x2026perhaps someone who targeted a few Terathan Matriarchs would do some damage to the Hive. That'd sure make my old mum proud....",
	[1073718] = L"To live among giants is no easy task my friend. Take these Titans. Their appetites are prodigious, indeed. They consume all in their path trying to placate their enormous hunger! It leaves precious little for us to feed ourselves. I may not be wealthy, but if someone could kill a few Titans, I could afford to be generous with them.",
	[1073719] = L"You've probably slain your fair share of the common orc, eh? Orcs are a dime a dozen, but the Orc Brute -- that's a different story entirely! They're hideous monsters who've earned their deaths a dozen times over! How about giving the lumpen oafs the death they so richly deserve?",
	[1073720] = L"Does it seem uncommonly warm here? I think it does. I've seen Fire Gargoyles nearby. Those burning wretches turn to ash everything they touch. Do you know what does for property values? Do us all a favor and fight fire with fire -- kill some Fire Gargoyles for me.",
	[1073721] = L"Beware the White Wyrm, my friend! They are not a beast to be trifled with. I've seen them gut villages and swallow peasants whole! My hatred for the albino atrocities runs deep -- so deep, I'd give all that I own to rid the land of them. ",
	[1073722] = L"Did you know Poison Elementals are corrupted from the very air? They are miserable wretches, cursed by foul magic. You do them a favor by destroying the noxious creatures -- they'd surely thank you, though you might not notice it for them trying to kill you. But, I could find it in my heart to reward you for killing poison elementals.",
	[1073723] = L"There is no greater foe than the mighty Dragon! A creature of myth and legend! A hero proves his worth by slaughtering the reptillian fiends! What? You're not swayed by my words? Well, would you be interested in a cash reward for killing dragons then?",
	[1073724] = L"Death all around us, like a plague of, uh, pestilence! Those undead magicians, the Liches, torment the living! And their masters, the Lich Lords are the worst of the bunch. I'll tell you, I'd give this large treasure pile to anyone who cleared these undead monsters!",
	[1073725] = L"Their girly bits are\x2026exposed! There, out in the open, for any child to see! A succubus is an affront to all decency and morality! Someone needs to stand up for the children! Someone needs to teach the succubi a lesson in decency!",
	[1028383] = L"Summon Water",
	[1073727] = L"The Lords of the Underworld have grown bold! They march across the land, terrorizing and rampaging! But without their leaders, the Balrons, the legions of the nether realms aren't nearly the threat. I could reward you handsomely if you could cut the head off of a demon army or two.",
	[1028384] = L"Circle 1",
	[1073729] = L"They say the Serpentine Dragons hail from far off lands. Well, that's just wrong. I mean, what, are native dragons supposed to compete with cheap foreign dragons? It's not fair! I think somebody should do something about it!",
	[1028385] = L"Circle 2",
	[1073731] = L"The older a wyrm gets, the more deadly and cunning. The Ancient Wyrms are a treacherous breed, each one soaked in the blood of innocents. A hero needs to right their wrongs, eradicate their evil from fair Britannia.",
	[1028386] = L"Circle 3",
	[1073733] = L"Perhaps you'll change your mind and return at some point.",
	[1028387] = L"Circle 4",
	[1073735] = L"Have you killed the Ophidian Knights or Avengers?",
	[1028388] = L"Circle 5",
	[1073737] = L"There's still too many unicorns around, if you catch my drift.",
	[1028389] = L"Circle 6",
	[1073739] = L"Did you forget to kill Giant Beetles?",
	[1028390] = L"Circle 7",
	[1073741] = L"There's too much cuteness in the world -- kill those pixies!",
	[1028391] = L"Circle 8",
	[1073743] = L"The chill won't lift until you eradicate a few Ice Elemenals.",
	[1028392] = L"ettin frame",
	[1073745] = L"Please, rid us of the Ant Lion infestation.",
	[1028393] = L"gorilla frame",
	[1073747] = L"I think someone should skin a few ratmen mages, eh?",
	[1028394] = L"lizardman frame",
	[1073749] = L"Please, help stop the Kraken menace.",
	[1028395] = L"ogre frame",
	[1073751] = L"Don't let the Nightmares or Fire Steeds continue to walk this earth.",
	[1028396] = L"troll frame",
	[1073753] = L"There's more Arctic Ogre Lords to kill, I'm sure of that.",
	[1028397] = L"male",
	[1073755] = L"The Daemon hordes still need to be thinned.",
	[1028398] = L"female",
	[1073757] = L"What are you looking at? Go kill Elder Gazers!",
	[1028399] = L"Bear Frame",
	[1073759] = L"I hope you haven't had your fill of killing Titans.",
	[1028400] = L"Rat Frame",
	[1073761] = L"Do not lose hope, you can face more Fire Gargoyles, I am certain.",
	[1028401] = L"Chicken Frame",
	[1073763] = L"I beseech you, put more Poison Elementals out of their misery.",
	[1028402] = L"Corpser Frame",
	[1073765] = L"Lich Lords still haunt our fair lands.",
	[1028403] = L"Demon Frame",
	[1073767] = L"There are plenty more Gargoyle Destroyers to, uh, destroy.",
	[1028404] = L"Deer Frame",
	[1073769] = L"Reduce a few more Skeletal Wyrms to a pile of bones.",
	[1028405] = L"Dog Frame",
	[1073771] = L"I can still smell the foul decay of Rotting Corpses. ",
	[1073772] = L"Fight the Ancient Wyrms, please!",
	[1073773] = L"Please, do no rest until those Sphinxes are properly schooled!<br>",
	[1073774] = L"You have finished your quest and may return for a reward.",
	[1073775] = L"Your quest is complete. Return for your reward.",
	[1073776] = L"We can all rest a little easier with less of those slithery Ophidians about. You've earned this reward.",
	[1073777] = L"The land appreciates your efforts with the Bog Things. We should have a bumper crop this year!",
	[1073778] = L"Okay, here's your reward. Now, we never spoke, did we?",
	[1073779] = L"Those Gargoyle fanatics won't be troubling anyone any time soon, eh?",
	[1073780] = L"Tell me, do the Giant Beetles crunch when you kill them? Well, here's your pay.",
	[1073781] = L"Ha! Blown away like smoke in the wind, those Efreets are! You earned this reward!",
	[1073782] = L"The world is a less magical place, with dead pixies. Good job.",
	[1073783] = L"Thinking about those eight legged monsters gives me the chills! Here, take this reward.",
	[1073784] = L"You snapped that cold spell, eh? For facing the Ice Elementals, here's a little something.",
	[1073785] = L"With the whipping vines thinned, farmers can get back to work.",
	[1073786] = L"The Ant Lion infestation seems reduced. Enjoy this reward then.",
	[1073787] = L"Reduced those Golems to component parts? Good, then -- you deserve this reward!",
	[1073788] = L"Ha, the furry wretches' magic was no match for you! A dead ratman mage is worth something, so enjoy!",
	[1073789] = L"The skies have been clear of drakes lately, so I guess you deserve a reward.",
	[1073790] = L"There's hasn't been a Kraken attack lately -- congratulations!",
	[1073791] = L"Trade is up fifteen percent since you attacked the Sand Vortexes. You've earned a share of the profit.",
	[1073792] = L"You've cleared the stables of evil, my friend! So here are your just rewards!",
	[1073793] = L"For your work against the lava snakes, I have a little something for you.",
	[1073794] = L"It'll be a cold day in you-know-where when you can't kill Artic Ogre Lords, eh?",
	[1073795] = L"I already feel the warmth returning. Accept this reward for killing Ice Fiends!",
	[1073796] = L"Sent them back where they belong, eh? Good work.",
	[1073797] = L"The world will not miss those blubbery brutes. For what you've done, enjoy this reward.",
	[1073798] = L"Don't look at me that way. Just take your reward and leave.",
	[1073799] = L"Mother will appreciate your fine work. Here, don't tell her I gave you this.",
	[1073800] = L"The shadow of Titans no longer stretches across the land. Thanks to you!",
	[1073801] = L"Thanks to you for stopping those orcish louts. You deserve this rich reward.",
	[1073802] = L"You have extinguished the gargoyle threat, traveler. Thanks to you.",
	[1073803] = L"Those pale monsters are no more. Enjoy the rewards of the just!",
	[1073804] = L"You have performed a noble service. Here, please take this reward.",
	[1073805] = L"Dragons mean treasure my friend -- enjoy this reward!",
	[1073806] = L"I can only hope these undead stay in their graves once and for all.",
	[1073807] = L"Thanks goodness someone thinks of the children. Enjoy this token of our esteem.",
	[1073808] = L"The gargoyle menace has been thwarted. Thank you, traveler.",
	[1073809] = L"You faced the hordes of the underworld and overcame. For that, I will be forever grateful.",
	[1073810] = L"With any luck, those dragons won't be back again!",
	[1073811] = L"You sent those foreign dragons packing, didn't you? My thanks!",
	[1073812] = L"The stench of decay subsides, thanks to you.",
