	[1074284] = L"Friend of the Fey",
	[1074285] = L"It is true that a skilled arcanist can summon and dominate an imp to serve at their pleasure.  To do such at thing though, you must master the miserable little fiends utterly by demonstrating your superiority.  Rough them up some -- kill a few.  That will do the trick.",
	[1074286] = L"The children of Sosaria understand the dedication and committment of an arcanist -- and will, from time to time offer their friendship.  If you would forge such a bond, first seek out a goodwill offering to present.  Pixies enjoy sweets and pretty things.",
	[1074287] = L"You're probably right.  They're not worth the effort.",
	[1074288] = L"There's always time to make new friends.",
	[1074289] = L"Surely you're not having difficulties swatting down those annoying pests?",
	[1074290] = L"I think honey and some sparkly beads would please a pixie.",
	[1074291] = L"Hah!  You showed them!",
	[1074292] = L"What have we here? Oh yes, gifts for a pixie.",
	[1074293] = L"Token of Friendship",
	[1074294] = L"Alliance",
	[1074295] = L"Cracking the Whip",
	[1074296] = L"Iron Will",
	[1074297] = L"I've wrapped your gift suitably to present to a pixie of discriminating taste.  Seek out Arielle and give her your offering.",
	[1074298] = L"*giggle* Mean reapers make pixies unhappy.  *light-hearted giggle*  You could fix them!",
	[1074299] = L"Elven Leafweave",
	[1074300] = L"Now that you've shown those mini pests your might, you should collect suitable implements to use to train your summoned pet.  I suggest a stout whip.",
	[1074301] = L"Hunter's Garb",
	[1074302] = L"Now you just need to make the little buggers fear you -- if you can slay an arcane daemon, you'll earn their subservience.",
	[1074303] = L"Plate of Honor",
	[1074304] = L"Assassin Armor",
	[1074305] = L"Death's Essence",
	[1074306] = L"Myrmidon Armor",
	[1074307] = L"Greymist Armor",
	[1074308] = L"Swiftflight (Marksman Set)",
	[1074309] = L"Evocaricus (Juggernaut Set)",
	[1074310] = L"I'll hold onto this gift in case you change your mind.",
	[1074311] = L"*giggle* Okies!",
	[1074312] = L"Maleki's Honor (Juggernaut Set)",
	[1074313] = L"Heh. Changed your mind, eh?",
	[1074314] = L"If you're not up for it, so be it.",
	[1074315] = L"Arielle wanders quite a bit, so I'm not sure exactly where to find her.  I'm sure she's going to love your gift.",
	[1074316] = L"Mean reapers are all around trees!  *giggle*  You fix them up, please.",
	[1074317] = L"Well, hurry up.  If you don't get a whip how do you expect to control the little devil?",
	[1074318] = L"You need to vanquish an arcane daemon before the imps will fear you properly.",
	[1074319] = L"*giggle*  Oooh!  For me?",
	[1074320] = L"*giggle* Mean reapers got fixed!  Pixie friend now! *giggle* When mean thingies bother you, a brave pixie will help.",
	[1074321] = L"That's a well-made whip.  No imp will ignore the sting of that lash.",
	[1074322] = L"You've demonstrated your strength, got a means of control, and taught the imps to fear you.  You're ready now to summon them.",
