	[1074355] = L"Strong Back",
	[1074356] = L"gift for arielle",
	[1074357] = L"Well, I don't mind saying it -- I'm flabbergasted!  Absolutely astonished.  I just heard that some elves want to convert themselves to humans through some magical process.  My cousin Nedrick does whatever needs doing.  I guess you could check it out for yourself if you're curious.  Anyway, I wonder if you'll bring my cousin, Drithen, this here treat my wife baked up for him special.",
