	[1028719] = L"unused",
	[1074399] = L"Seek the Huntsman, the centuar tasked with maintaining the balance.  And lastly seek Arielle, the pixie, who has perhaps the most important lesson -- not to take yourself too seriously.",
	[1028720] = L"crystal",
	[1074401] = L"You are bald!",
	[1028721] = L"crystal",
	[1074403] = L"Greetings, traveler and welcome.",
	[1028722] = L"crystal",
	[1074405] = L"Elves and humans; we lived together once in peace.  Mighty relics that attest to our friendship remain, of course.  Yet, memories faded when the Gem was shattered and the world torn asunder.  Alone in The Heartwood, our elven brothers and sisters wondered what terrible evil had befallen Sosaria.",
	[1028723] = L"crystal",
	[1074407] = L"But you must prove yourself to me.  Humans possess a strength of character and back.  Humans are quick-witted and able to pick up a smattering of nearly any talent.  Humans are tough both mentally and physically.  And of course, humans defend their own -- sometimes with their own lives.",
	[1028724] = L"crystal",
	[1074409] = L"Seek out a human in need and prove your worth as a defender of humanity.  Seek Belulah in Nu'Jelm and heartily challenge the elements in a display of toughness to rival any human.",
	[1028725] = L"crystal",
	[1074411] = L"Or turn away and embrace your heritage.  It matters not to me.",
	[1028726] = L"crystal",
	[1074413] = L"You must yet perform these deeds: ",
	[1028727] = L"crystal",
	[1074415] = L"Brine shrimp",
