	[1028778] = L"willow tree",
	[1074517] = L"Special Treat for Drithen",
	[1028779] = L"willow tree",
	[1074519] = L"Ho there!  There's nothing quite like a day's honest labor to make you appreciate being alive.  Hey, maybe you'd like to help out with this project?  These crates need to be delivered to Sledge.  The only thing is -- it's a bit of a rush job and if you don't make it in time, he won't take them.  Can I trust you to help out?",
	[1028780] = L"oak tree",
	[1074521] = L"Oh yah, if you're too busy, no problem.",
	[1028781] = L"oak tree",
	[1074523] = L"Hey, if you have cargo for me, you can start unloading over here.",
	[1028782] = L"demon skull",
	[1074525] = L"I hope my grandfather will be alright.",
	[1028783] = L"demon skull",
	[1074527] = L"It's all about hardship, suffering, struggle and pain.  Without challenges, you've got nothing to test yourself against -- and that's what life is all about.  Self improvement!  Honing your body and mind!  Overcoming obstacles ... You'll see what I mean if you take on my challenge.",
	[1028784] = L"demon skull",
	[1074529] = L"You're not making much progress in the honing-mind-and-body department, are you?",
	[1028785] = L"demon skull",
	[1074531] = L"The first time you were born, you entered the world bare of all possessions and concerns.  So too as you transform to your new life as a human, you must remove all worldly goods from the touch of your flesh.",
	[1028786] = L"book of chivalry",
	[1074533] = L"Fragment of a Map",
	[1074534] = L"The Ancient World",
	[1074535] = L"The lore of my people mentions Mondain many times.  In one tale, it is revealed that he created and enslaved a race -- a sort of man bull, known as a 'minotaur'.  The tales speak of mighty warriors who charged with blood-soaked horns into the heat of battle.  But, alas, the fate of the bull-men is unknown after the rupture.  Will you seek information about their civilization?",
	[1074536] = L"Warriors of the Gemkeeper",
	[1074537] = L"Here we honor the Gemkeeper's Apprentice and seek to aid her efforts against the humans responsible for the death of her teacher -- and the destruction of the elven way of life.  Our tales speak of a fierce race of servants of the Gemkeeper, the men-bulls whose battle-skill was renowned.  It is desireable to discover the fate of these noble creatures after the Rupture.  Will you seek information?",
	[1074538] = L"I am disappointed, but I respect your decision.",
	[1074539] = L"A traveler has told me that worshippers of Mondain still exist and wander the land.  Perhaps their lore speaks of whether the bull-men survived.  I do not think they share their secrets gladly.  You may need to be 'persuasive'.",
	[1074540] = L"I care not how you get the information.  Kill as many humans as you must ... but find the fate of the minotaurs.  Perhaps another of the Gemkeeper's servants has the knowledge we seek.",
	[1074541] = L"You have discovered an important clue!",
	[1074542] = L"What have you found?",
	[1074543] = L"The Golden Horn",
	[1074544] = L"Close Enough",
	[1074545] = L"Ah ha!  You see here ... and over here ... The map fragment places the city of the bull-men, Labyrinth, on that piece of Sosaria that was thrown into the sky.  Hmmm, I would have you go there and find any artifacts that remain that help tell the story.  But, legend speaks of a mighty barrier to prevent invasion of the city.  Take this map to Braen and explain the problem. Perhaps he can devise a solution.",
	[1074546] = L"Ah ha!  You see here ... and over here ... The map fragment places the city of the bull-men, Labyrinth, on that piece of Sosaria that was thrown into the sky.  Hmmm, I would have you go there and seek out these warriors to see if they might join our cause.  But, legend speaks of a mighty barrier to prevent invasion of the city.  Take this map to Canir and explain the problem. Perhaps she can devise a solution.<br>",
	[1074547] = L"Braen is nearby, run and speak with him.",
	[1074548] = L"Canir is nearby, run and speak with her.",
	[1074549] = L"Yes?  What do you want?  I'm very busy.",
	[1074550] = L"Bullish",
	[1074551] = L"Taking the Bull by the Horns",
	[1074552] = L"Oh, I see. I will need some materials to infuse you with the essence of a bull-man, so you can fool their defenses.  The most similar beast to the original Baratarian bull that the minotaur were bred from is undoubtedly the mighty Gaman, native to the Lands of the Feudal Lords.  I need horns, in great quantity to undertake this magic.",
	[1074553] = L"Interesting.  I believe I have a way.  I will need some materials to infuse you with the essence of a bull-man, so you can fool their defenses.  The most similar beast to the original Baratarian bull that the minotaur were bred from is undoubtedly the mighty Gaman, native to the Lands of the Feudal Lords.  I need horns, in great quantity to undertake this magic.",
	[1074554] = L"Oh come now, don't be afraid.  The magic won't harm you.",
	[1074555] = L"I cannot grant you the ability to pass through the bull-men's defenses without the gaman horns.",
	[1074556] = L"You've returned at last!  Give me just a moment to examine what you've brought and I can perform the magic that will allow you enter the Labyrinth.",
	[1074557] = L"Gaman Horns",
	[1074558] = L"That doesn't look very appealing.",
	[1074559] = L"It looks unappetizing, but you're hungry...",
	[1074560] = L"recipe scroll",
	[1074561] = L"Portal to Yew",
	[1074562] = L"Portal to Heartwood",
	[1074563] = L"You haven't forged a friendship with the fey and are unable to summon their aid.",
	[1074564] = L"You haven't demonstrated mastery to summon a fiend.",
	[1074565] = L"The acid river burns your skin.",
	[1028803] = L"curse weapon",
	[1074567] = L"The acid river is much stronger here. You realize that allowing the acid to touch your flesh will surely kill you.",
	[1028804] = L"evil omen",
	[1074569] = L"Slayers of innocent souls are not welcome to enter here!",
	[1028805] = L"horrific beast",
	[1074571] = L"Captain Blackheart's Fishing Pole",
	[1028806] = L"lich form",
	[1074573] = L"Mistaken Identity",
	[1028807] = L"mind rot",
	[1074575] = L"You have activated this object!",
	[1028808] = L"pain spike",
	[1074577] = L"Food Added: ~1_CUR~ Needed: ~2_NEED~ ",
	[1028809] = L"poison strike",
	[1074579] = L"Yes, can I help you?",
	[1028810] = L"strangle",
	[1074581] = L"Well hello there. Oh.  Wait a minute, you're not here to plead the case of that traitor Danoel are you?",
	[1028811] = L"summon familiar",
	[1074583] = L"Isn't that interesting?  Someone was willing to pay a lot of gold to see me gone.  You've earned a reward for bringing this to me.",
	[1028812] = L"vampiric embrace",
	[1074585] = L"Probably a wise choice to keep a low profile.",
	[1028813] = L"vengeful spirit",
	[1074587] = L"*smile* Greetings!  Oh ... oh my.  Oh, goodness ... *startled gasp*  Did you read ... we must report this at once.",
	[1028814] = L"wither",
