	[1075392] = L"Honest Beggar",
	[1075393] = L"Beg pardon, sir. I mean, madam. Uh, can I ask a favor of you? I found this jeweled ring.  Most people would sell it and keep the money, but not me. I ain't never stole nothing, and I ain't about to start. I tried to take it over to Brit castle, figgerin' it must belong to some highborn lady, but the guards threw me out. You look like they might let you pass. Will you take the ring over there and see if you can find the owner?",
	[1075394] = L"Find the ring\x2019s owner.",
	[1075395] = L"I see. Too good to help an honest beggar like me, eh?",
	[1075396] = L"A jewel like this must be worth a lot, so it must belong to some noble or another. I would show it around the castle. Someone\x2019s bound to recognize it.",
	[1075397] = L"Didst thou find my ring? I thank thee very much! It is an old ring, and a gift from my husband. I was most distraught when I realized it was missing.",
	[1075398] = L"Regina\x2019s Thanks",
	[1075399] = L"What\x2019s that you say? It was a humble beggar that found my ring? Such honesty must be rewarded. Here, take this packet and return it to him, and I will be in your debt.",
	[1075400] = L"Transparent Heart",
	[1075401] = L"Hmph. Very well. What did you say his name was?",
	[1075402] = L"Take the packet and return it to the beggar who found my ring.",
	[1075403] = L"What? For me? Let me see . . . these sapphire earrings are for you, it says. Oh, she wants to offer me a job! This is the most wonderful thing that ever happened to me! ",
	[1075404] = L"Doughty Warriors",
	[1075405] = L"You did great work. Thanks to you, my puppies are training harder than ever. I think they could actually take a mongbat now. I\x2019m still worried they\x2019ll slack off, though. What say you to slaying some Imps for me now? Show them how it\x2019s really done?",
	[1075406] = L"Show them what a real warrior is REALLY made of!",
	[1075407] = L"You\x2019re pretty sad. When I was a young warrior, I wasn\x2019t one to walk away from a challenge.",
	[1075408] = L"You won\x2019t find many imps on this continent. Mostly, they\x2019re native to Ilshenar. Might be a few up around the hedge maze east of Skara Brae, though.",
	[1075409] = L"Hah! I knew you were up to the challenge.",
	[1029225] = L"fan",
	[1075411] = L"You\x2019ve really inspired my trainees. They\x2019re working harder than ever. I\x2019ve got one more request for you, and it\x2019s a big one. Those mongbats didn\x2019t pose a problem. You mowed down the imps with no trouble. But do you dare take on a couple of daemons?",
	[1029226] = L"fan",
	[1075413] = L"What? You\x2019re not scared of a couple of lousy daemons, are you?",
	[1029227] = L"fan",
	[1075415] = L"Thanks for helping me out. You\x2019re a real hero to my guards. Valor is its own reward, but maybe you wouldn\x2019t mind wearing this sash. We don\x2019t give these out to just anyone, you know!",
	[1029228] = L"fan",
	[1075417] = L"I beg your pardon, but will you listen to my story? My family, the de Boors family, have been jewel traders as far back as anyone can remember. Alas, by the time I was born, we had fallen on hard times. <br>To survive, I have had to sell much of my family\x2019s property. Most of it was meaningless, but I regret that a few years ago I made a terrible mistake. I pawned a shield bearing my family\x2019s coat of arms to a loan shark. That shield was borne into battle by Jaan de Boors, the founder of our house! It has no value to anyone, but that blackguard won\x2019t believe I have no money. He wants a fortune in jewels before he will return it.<br>Now I have learned that I am dying. Soon I will be gone, and my lineage with me. For the sake of what little honor is left to me and my family name, I cannot bear to leave our ancestral shield in the hands of that villain. Will you help me recover it?<br>",
	[1029229] = L"painting",
	[1075419] = L"I know how much I am asking. Please, can you not help a dying man restore his family\x2019s honor?",
	[1029230] = L"painting",
	[1075421] = L"You have done it! Bless you! I do appreciate this very much! Though, will you do me one last favor?",
	[1029231] = L"painting",
	[1075423] = L"Will you take the jewels to the loan shark? I am not well enough to go myself, though it is not far.",
	[1029232] = L"painting",
	[1075425] = L"Ah well. You have already helped me by gathering the jewels. I cannot complain.",
	[1029233] = L"painting",
	[1075427] = L"What do you want? Oh, that jewel merchant wants his shield back, eh?",
	[1029234] = L"painting",
	[1075429] = L"That idiot! This beat up piece of junk isn\x2019t worth more than three gold coins, four at most! Oh, well, a deal\x2019s a deal!",
	[1029235] = L"painting",
	[1075431] = L"I don\x2019t care what you do!",
	[1029236] = L"painting",
	[1075433] = L"My shield! My family\x2019s honor! You have my gratitude. Please, take this goblet. It is small enough repayment for all you have done for me, but it is the only thing of my family\x2019s that I have left.",
	[1029237] = L"painting",
