	[1075783] = L"*smiles* Surely thy deeds will be recognized by those who see thee wearing this shield! It shall serve as a reminder of the exalted path that thou hast journeyed upon, and I wish to thank thee on behalf of all whom thine efforts shall benefit. Ah, let us not forget that old cloak I gavest thee - I shall take it back now and give thee thine reward.",
