	[1077443] = L"The Book of Truth has been stolen! 'Tis said that the dark entities from beyond our world are behind this evil deed, and to keep us from finding it, they've made lots of copies. My twin sister and I have made a pledge to help return the book to safety, but I'm afraid that we wouldn't be very useful in the dungeons. We're going to help Mistress Menzzobaanea examine any of the copies that you can bring us, and I promise to give you a small reward for each one that you bring to me. ",
