	[1149627] = L"Clean",
	[1032190] = L"cave drawings",
	[1112917] = L"*Axem appears to be studying an old scroll*<br><br>...if I take the third letter in every tenth word, then add them together backwards, I should... Oh, hello there, I didn't see you come in. You look like an adventurous type, perhaps you have come across things in your travels that might look like bits of junk. Things like broken pottery laying around. I'm sure you have, but did not know what you were looking for.<br><br>I'll tell you what, if you bring me some ancient pottery fragments, I'll see what I can dig up for your trouble. What do you say?",
	[1032191] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149625] = L"That cannot be made into a trophy.",
	[1032192] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149624] = L"You can't reach the lava there.",
	[1032193] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149623] = L"What lava do you want to fish in?",
	[1032194] = L"cave drawings",
	[1112919] = L"I really need at least ten fragments to be able to glean anything useful from them. Please come back when you have ten.",
	[1032195] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149621] = L"You need to be closer to the lava to fish!",
	[1032196] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149620] = L"<CENTER>Aft Starboard Cannon Control</CENTER>",
	[1032197] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149619] = L"<CENTER>Aft Port Cannon Control</CENTER>",
	[1032198] = L"cave drawings",
	[1112921] = L"*As you approach, Axem seems completely unaware of you*<br><br>Ok, now if I substitute each symbol by the one thirteen places in front of it, I get... what? Who are... oh, my, forgive me. Greetings! It is good to see you again. I must apologize, I have been so busy trying to figure out the meaning of the symbols on the pottery fragments you brought me. So far, I have not gotten very far, but perhaps if I were able to cross reference these symbols with another source.<br><br>Let me think... yes, I think that would do. Have you seen any remnants of old scrolls laying about during your travels? I would reward you, of course, if you would bring them to me. Is it a deal?",
	[1032199] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149617] = L"<CENTER>Amidships Port Cannon Control</CENTER>",
	[1032200] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149616] = L"<CENTER>Forward Starboard Cannon Control</CENTER>",
	[1032201] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149615] = L"<CENTER>Forward Port Cannon Control</CENTER>",
	[1032202] = L"cave drawings",
	[1112923] = L"I will need at least five remnants of an ancient scroll to be able to piece together anything useful from it.",
	[1032203] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149613] = L"Dry Dock Boat",
	[1032204] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149612] = L"The vessel resists your spell.",
	[1032205] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149611] = L"You don't have enough money to pay the entry fee.",
	[1032206] = L"cave drawings",
	[1112925] = L"*As you approach Axem, you realize that he is looking right at you for a change*<br><br>You thought you would sneak up on me again, did you? I saw you coming, so you will have to find amusement elsewhere today.<br><br>Alas, I could use your help though. I believe that I have the meanings for some of the symbols found on these ancient fragments, there is some relation to our modern alphabet, but there is just too much that has changed to say with absolute certainty.<br><br>While you were off gallivanting about, have you noticed any old tomes in out of the way places? We have a few here already, but they've already been translated and are not from the same era as the rest of what you have brought me. These bits and pieces will only allow me to get so far, I'm afraid. If you know where to find anything like that, will you bring it to me?",
	[1032207] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149609] = L"You have paid the entry fee from your bank account.",
	[1032208] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149608] = L"Since your bank box and backpack were full, the entry fee wasn't refunded.",
	[1032209] = L"cave drawings",
	[1149607] = L"The entry fee has been refunded to your backpack.",
	[1032210] = L"cave drawings",
	[1112927] = L"Are you going to bring me an untranslated ancient tome, or not? Now, where did I put my magnifying glass...",
