	[1032495] = L"leaves",
	[1115407] = L"The right to rule is earned by conquest, not by paying lip service to an archaic system of virtues or by paying bribes. There is little hope in praying for the return of a long-departed king and yearning for the return of a golden age long past. Power lies not with the common man but with the warlords who will rise up and seize it. These are the truths the Guardian teaches.",
	[1032496] = L"leaves",
	[1115405] = L"Only by living by the Three Principles and the Eight Virtues may we as a society bring about a return to our former glory. We must walk strong and not be set astray by those who would put the individual above the community or who mask their greed and lust for power behind a facade of open dealings. Our bravery, our passion, and our pursuit of truth will deliver us from chaos!",
	[1032497] = L"leaves",
	[1115403] = L"Come in, come in! Uskadesh told me you were coming.",
	[1032498] = L"leaves",
	[1115401] = L"Ah, you're back.  Wait... why are you back?<br><br>Let's go through it again, shall we?  You need a lantern (NOTE: make sure the lantern is turned off or he won't take it... he's just like that), a draconic orb from the abyss, cherry blossoms from the shrine of Isamu, and a flaming bud from the cyclops in the Lost lands.",
