	[1153993] = L"Why hello there! If Armor Refinement techniques are what you seek, then ye come to the right place!  There are two basic components that can be used to craft an Armor Refinement. First you must collect either a wash or a cure. Should ye wish to increase the luster of the material, enhancing the wearer\x2019s chance of defense then wash is what ye seek. If it is protection from the elements then cure can be used to seal the material. Once ye have these components in hand simply use them with sufficient raw materials to create Threads. These threads can be applied in me shop here to the appropriate piece of armor.",
