	[1035883] = L"Field of Poison",
	[1154262] = L"A Note from Cousteau Perron...",
	[1154263] = L"Now that you have done what I asked, I shall do what you ask of me. Before you may continue your adventure you'll need to collect the components of the suit.  I have listed the components and whom you might seek to acquire them from below. Return to see Hepler Paulson in the City of Trinsic when you've got everything!<BR><BR>Nictitating Lenses - Josef Skimmons, the Master Blacksmith at the Cutlass Smithing in Bucaneer's Den will surely know how to craft such a thing.<BR><BR>Canvass Robe - Madeline Harte, Seamstress at the Adventurer's Needle in Jhelom is well known for her prowess with a needle.  If anyone can craft this for you, it is her.<BR><BR>Aqua Pendant - Zalia the Gemologist, in her craft few are better.  She will surely be able to supply the pendant. She can be found at the Gypsy camp in Northeastern Ilshenar.<BR><BR>Boots of Ballast - Champ Huthwait, a seedy man to say the least but a fine cobbler.  Seek him at the Adventurer's Supply in Vesper.",
	[501562] = L"You have been suspended by the Thieves Guild.",
	[1154265] = L"*You carefully examine the garment. The fabric is shredded and chewed.*",
	[1154266] = L"*You inspect the boots closely. The soles are quite worn.  You discern whomever was wearing them did quite a bit of running.*",
	[1154267] = L"*Upon closer inspection the blade shows signs of dragon blood dried upon the hilt.*",
	[501563] = L"This magic item is out of charges.",
	[1154269] = L"Map to an Unknown Shipwreck",
	[1154270] = L"*You unfurl the map and study it carefully. You recognize Gravewater Lake. In the center of the lake is a large X*",
	[1154271] = L"Jack O' Lantern Carving Kit",
	[501564] = L"This magic item is out of charges.",
	[1154273] = L"What do you wish to carve?",
	[1154274] = L"*You aren't quite sure what to do with this. If you spoke to the Salvage Master at the Sons of the Sea in Trinsic you might have a better understanding of its use...*",
	[1154275] = L"Only Citizens of this City may use this. ",
	[501565] = L"You can't see that object well enough to identify it.",
	[1154277] = L"Open Inventory",
	[1154278] = L"Place Ballot Box",
	[1154279] = L"Greetings! My have my pockets become burdened with gold! Not that this is a bad thing of course...*grins*  So ye seek to cash in salvaging many wrecks that now litter the sea floor? Well I'll tell you what...buy some of this here salvage gear and go find yerself a wreck.  Return to me when ye have a piece o' wreckage.",
	[501566] = L"This magic item is out of charges.",
	[1154281] = L"Almost uncanny how many wrecks now dot the seascape, none can say for sure why there are so many as of late...sure a drunk skipper here or there will bring a ship down quick...but this...well why question good fortune I always say!",
	[1154282] = L"How do I use salvage gear?",
	[1154283] = L"Buy a salvage hook from me, head to deep water and hoist the hook overboard.  With any luck you'll pull out a bit o' wreckage and if fortune smiles on you, a bit o' treasure too!",
	[501567] = L"REL WIS",
	[1154285] = L"Who is the Master Tinker?",
	[1154286] = L"I've only heard they live in East Britain, if ye find them I bet ye may convince em to tell you of the suit!",
	[1154287] = L"*She looks up from the slowly rotating rabbit on a spit* Oh hello there, what brings you way out to this frozen tundra?",
	[501568] = L"For whatever reason, the person helping you has decided to defer you to someone else.",
	[1154289] = L"Ahh, been listening to old Hepler have you?  So I've heard something of these shipwrecks, even all the way out here.  I'm guessing you want me to tell you of one of these suits to help you explore beneath the waves?",
	[1154290] = L"Do you know of the suit?",
	[1154291] = L"Before I will help you with this perhaps you can assist me with a small task?  I require an Ice Wyrm Scale to assist me in my research, but sadly I am not strong enough to slay one alone.  Do you think you could collect this for me? Yes? Oh grand! Return to me with the ice wyrm scale and I will assist thee further.",
	[501569] = L"The next available companion will assist you.",
	[1154293] = L"This is exactly what I was talking about! How did you ever find such a thing! No matter! *reads the plans carefully*  It\x2019s all here by golly, detailed instructions on how to craft each item.  There are a number of professionals throughout the realm who will be able to assist you in crafting such things \x2013 I\x2019ve written them down on this list here *hands you a note* Simply seek the professionals I have listed and you should be well on your way!",
	[1154294] = L"Hello there...what\x2019s this? *reads the note* Look at these lenses! Cousteau drew these up did she...hrmm\x2026well in any case I might be able to craft these lenses if you would be willing to assist me...",
	[1154295] = L"What do you need assistance with?",
	[501570] = L"The person helping you has disconnected from the game for some reason.",
	[1154297] = L"An orcish machine?",
	[1154298] = L"Yes! That\x2019s exactly what I\x2019m talking about! Drill baby drill! You get me some schematics to make that machine and I\x2019ll strike your lenses for you...I bet those Orcs are holed up in their cave outside Yew.",
	[1154299] = L"Great work! *Reading the schematic*  Excellent!  This is just what I need to give me a leg up on the competition! As promised here are those lenses you requested!",
	[501571] = L"The next available companion will pick up where they left off.",
	[1154301] = L"Willem went to Destard?",
	[1154302] = L"Oh! You\x2019ve found his hat! Did you...*pauses and appears to begin to cry but regains her composure\x201d Oh, I see.  At least he showed Valor...I thank you for give me closure.  I had a chance to read the note from Cousteau, this should be what you need.",
	[1154303] = L"Just tell him I'll have the money by...*pauses*...*with a smile*...Oh, you aren't part of Mercutio's crew?  Oh well then, what's your business then? Loafers? Sandals? A Fine pair of boots then? ",
	[501572] = L"pointPlayerToLocation called: 1",
	[1154305] = L"*reads the note*  Well I see you and Cousteau are after that suit then.  Well I'll tell you what I tell everyone else...if you want the Boots of Ballast you need to help me out with a sticky situation.",
	[1154306] = L"What kind of sticky situation?",
	[1154307] = L"Yea, that's right.  Seems Mercutio's Gang is after me for a bit of a...disagreement about a small debt...if you were to...take care of Mercutio's gang I'd be willing to hook you up with those boots.",
	[501573] = L"The arrow shall guide you during your quest.",
	[1154309] = L"They usually hangout just southwest of the City in some old ruins.  Bring me evidence of Mercutio's demise and I will get you the boots you seek. ",
	[1154310] = L"You did it! Hot diggity! Looks like I won't have to deal with that knave any longer! Smooth sailing from here on out...just me and the tables...oh, right here are your boots!",
	[1154311] = L"Hello zere my darling - looking for something shiny? Zalia has just vhat you are looking for!",
	[501574] = L"Your quest has been cancelled!",
	[1154313] = L"*Reads the note from Cousteau*  Oh another one of you zhen eh?  Zha Aqua pendant!  Might as well ask for zha crown jewels! I will craft zhis jewel for you if you acquire zha correct gemstone!",
	[1154314] = L"Where do I find such a gemstone?",
	[1154315] = L"Zha Aqua Gem! And I vhant a loaf of bread filled with gold!  *laughs* Oh, you vhere serious?  Well zhen ye must wrestle one avay from zhe Djinn.",
	[501575] = L"Your quest has been cancelled!",
	[1035911] = L"Field of fire",
	[1154318] = L"Ahah! Yes, yes, zhat is indeed zhe gem! *does some quick tinkering*  Here is your pendant as you vish...",
