	[1154406] = L"<I>*The letters are sealed in tubes capped with wax to make them waterproof and hidden away. Written on the outside is \x201cOpen only on the occasion of the death of Champ Huthwait, to be delivered to the Britain Bugle, the Trinsic Tribune, and the Sosarian Scout.\x201d*</I>",
	[1035956] = L"tiller man",
	[501598] = L"You hear the music and realize that the musician is trying to get you angry...!",
	[1035957] = L"tiller man",
	[1154410] = L"Been a good couple of days out near Valor, finding all sorts of new gemstones for pieces! I don't know if I be finding anything to beat that little piece I sold to that lad Ethan, but most aren't so dead set on such a ring either. Lucky lass he got!<BR><BR>A shame I can't deal with those blasted Djinns meself...They be holding the gems I need for making those fancy pendants. Maybe I'll find some fool blasted stupid enough to be getting it for me.<BR><BR>Made a trade with those others who live over near Compassion, and managed to get a good profit from it! Pity they didn't know the difference between a citrine and an amber, but ain't no skin off me own nose.<BR><BR>Shame the crystalline blackrock our miners dig up is so easily broken...ain't no use for gemcrafting or jewelry making at all.<BR><BR>",
	[1035958] = L"dragon prow",
	[501599] = L"Your music fails to incite enough anger.",
