	[1074586] = L"It might be safest to deliver the letter to someone trustworthy that isn't too important.  Sarakki the Notary might be a good choice.",
	[502183] = L"Your brain feels like it is on fire!",
	[1074584] = L"You have discovered a private letter from the sorceress Minax to her dear friend \"Travesty\" that implicates some very important people in her pay.  Will you risk drawing attention to yourself by delivering the bundle to the castle in Britain?<br>",
	[1074582] = L"Ah!  You found my property.  Thank you for your honesty in returning it to me.",
	[1074580] = L"Is that my bucket? I had to ditch my favorite bucket when a group of ratmen jumped me!",
	[502184] = L"Bleargh, this potion seems to have spoiled.",
	[1074578] = L"Water Added: ~1_CUR~ Needed: ~2_NEED~",
	[1074576] = L"The cold energy from the pool penetrates your skin and coalesces in your bones.",
	[1074574] = L"What do you want?  Wonderful, another whining request for a refund on tuition.  You know, experiences like that are invaluable ... and infrequent.  Having the opportunity to test yourself under such realistic situations isn't something the college offers all students.  Fine. Fine.  You'll need to submit a refund request form in triplicate before I can return your 1,000,000 gold tuition.  You'll need to get some signatures and a few other odds and ends.",
