	[1074528] = L"My way of life isn't for everyone, that's true enough.",
	[1074526] = L"Grandfather's farm is a ways west of the Shrine of Spirituality. So, we're not quite there yet.  Thank you again for keeping me safe.",
	[1074524] = L"Oh!  I just don't know what to do.  My mother is away and my father told me not to talk to strangers ... *worried frown*  But my grandfather has sent word that he has been hurt and needs me to tend his wounds.  He has a small farm southeast of here.  Would you ... could you ... escort me there safely?",
