	[1074466] = L"Monstrous Interred Grizzle Armor",
	[1074464] = L"mounted Dread Horn",
	[1074462] = L"The best thing about my job is that I do a little bit of everything, every day.  It's what we're good at really.  Just picking up something and making it do something else.  Listen, I'm really low on parts.  Are you interested in fetching me some supplies?",
	[502205] = L"You are already affected by this.",
	[1074460] = L"If I knew where my cousin was, I'd make the delivery myself.",
	[1074458] = L"Be careful down there. I don't like losing customers.",
	[1074456] = L"I sure don't want to go down there either.  You won't hear me chiding you. In fact, I commend your intellect.",
	[502206] = L"You are already affected by this.",
	[1074454] = L"Watch Your Step",
	[1074452] = L"What kind of adventurer are you that you can't afford to outlay some gold on good equipment.  You'll need this machete to get under those roots.  It's a good price.",
	[1074450] = L"Ho there!  If you wish to cross and test yourself in the Blighted Grove, you'll need a special machete.  Luckily I have one right here and it's for sale!  Only 1,000 gold each.",
	[502207] = L"You must have a free hand to drink a potion.",
	[1074448] = L"Step right up!  Thank you, enjoy the amazing caverns.",
	[1074446] = L"C'mon now Lords and Ladies -- you're passing up the opportunity of a lifetime.  Is 10,000 gold too much to pay for your enlightenment?",
	[1074444] = L"Wonders of the Natural World",
	[502208] = L"Checking for an owner.",
	[1074442] = L"Most of the creatures here wouldn't be interested in my thesis.  *nervous chuckle*  Master Gnosos would argue that no one is -- not even the undead.  Still, I'd wager that the more powerful undead have my pages.",
	[1074440] = L"Disintegrating Thesis Notes",
	[1074438] = L"Misplaced",
	[502209] = L"I have an owner...",
	[1074436] = L"Until my sisters have been treated with mercy and released from their twisted existence and until the vile Saliva is slain, I cannot feel safe or bestow my blessing.",
	[1074434] = L"Oh help! Help me!  I don't want to end up like my sisters, enslaved by the cruel Melisande.  I cannot flee, I am bound here by the evil of the harpy Saliva.  Won't you please help me and redeem my sisters at the same time?  I will grant you my blessing in return.",
	[1074432] = L"Vacation days: ~1_DAYS~",
	[502210] = L"...but it's not you!",
