	[502213] = L"Can't make you an owner, since you're already an owner.",
	[1074412] = L"You have made a good start but have more yet to do.",
	[1074410] = L"You have proven yourself capable and commited and so I will grant you the transformation you seek.",
	[1074408] = L"Seek Sledge the Versatile and learn about human ingenuity and creativity.  Seek Patricus and demonstrate your integrity and strength.",
	[502214] = L"You're holding me, so I'm yours!",
	[1074406] = L"Violent change marked the sundering of our ties.  We are different -- elves and humans.  And yet we are much alike.  I can give an elf the chance to walk as a human upon Sosaria.  I can undertake the transformation.",
	[1074404] = L"Perhaps you have heard of the service I offer?  Perhaps you wish to avail yourself of the opportunity I lay before you.",
	[1074402] = L"Special Hair Dye",
	[502215] = L"Nobody else owns me, so you can have me.",
	[1074400] = L"Or do none of these things.  You must choose your own path in the world, and what use you'll make of your existence.",
	[1074398] = L"Seek Strongroot, the great treefellow, whose very roots reach to the heart of the world.  Seek Enigma, whose wisdom can only be conveyed in riddles and rhymes.  Seek Bravehorn, the great hart, who exemplifies the fierce dedication of a protector of his people.",
	[1074396] = L"This special hair dye is made of a unique mixture of leaves, permanently changing one's hair color until another dye is used.",
