	[1072672] = L"Unknown Potion",
	[1072674] = L"Mangy, lice encrusted furballs!  Those filthy ratmen have been sneaking into camp again, the signs are obvious.  They've fouled the water stores again and stolen what they couldn't eat.  Are you up to cleaning up the rat warrens?  ",
	[502279] = L"No selection.",
	[1072676] = L"You may only transport your corpse while you are still dead.",
	[1072678] = L"You have awakened the master of this realm. You need to hurry to defeat it in time!",
	[1072680] = L"You have been given the key to the boss.",
	[502280] = L"You can't putrify that!",
	[1072682] = L"This is not the proper key.",
	[1072684] = L"I understand.  The stench in those tunnels is unbearable.",
	[1072686] = L"What a miserable place we live in.  Look around you at the changes we've wrought. The trees are sprouting leaves once more and the grass is reclaiming the blood-soaked soil.  Who would have imagined we'd find ourselves here?  Our \"neighbors\" are anything but friendly and those ogres are the worst of the lot.  Maybe you'd be interested in helping our community by disposing of some of our least amiable neighbors?",
	[502281] = L"Initializing quest egg.",
	[1072688] = L"You can't miss those ogres, they're huge and just outside the gates here.",
	[1072690] = L"Token of Love",
	[1072692] = L"The Brains of the Operation",
	[502282] = L"Failed to find NPCs near quest egg, aborting.",
	[1072694] = L"The Bigger They Are ...",
	[1072696] = L"The unblessed failed.  Make sure there is room in your pack for the deed.",
	[1072698] = L"Argh!  I knew those ratmen were up to no good!  They have stolen the ring I was making for my beloved Ciala.  The sparkle must have caught their greedy eyes.  Find the ring please!  I beg you.",
	[502283] = L"Adding a new quest: order.",
	[1072700] = L"The stolen ring is easy enough to recognize.  It has an inscription on it declaring my love for Ciala.  Please find this token of love for me!",
	[1072702] = L"I know that this is a lot to ask.  Thank you for hearing my request.",
	[1072704] = L"My beloved Ciala is the most wonderful, most perfect, most delightful woman.  Please bring her the token quickly!  I can't bear the wait for her joyous response.",
	[502284] = L"Failed to find a protagonist.",
	[1072706] = L"A large bag of treasure.",
	[1072708] = L"Reluctance doesn't become a hero like you.  But, as you wish.",
	[1072710] = L"Inconceiveable!  We've learned that the ogre leadership has recruited some heavy-duty guards to their cause.  I've never personally fought a cyclopian warrior, but I'm sure you could easily best a few and report back how much trouble they'll cause to our growing community?",
	[502285] = L"I am already an actor!",
	[1072712] = L"Make sure you fully assess all of the cyclopian tactical abilities!",
	[1072714] = L"Certainly.  You've done enough to merit a breather.  When you're ready for more, report back to me.",
	[1072716] = L"Friends of the Library",
	[502286] = L"I am now a quest actor!",
	[1072718] = L"The Secret Ingredient",
	[1072720] = L"Shhh!  *angry whisper*  This is a library, not some bawdy house!  If you wish to become a friend of the library you'll learn to moderate your volume.  And, of course, you'll take this application and have it notarized by Sarakki the Notary.  Until you've become an official friend of the library, I can't allow you to make donations.  It wouldn't be proper.",
	[1072722] = L"*glare*  Shhhh!  You need to visit the notary.  She can be found near the castle.",
	[502287] = L"Entered completeQuest",
	[1072724] = L"What do you have there?  Oh.  *look of dismay*  It seems everyone is interested in helping the library -- but no one warned me to stock up on sealing wax.  I'm afraid I'm out of the mixture we use to notarize offical documents.  There will be a delay ... unless you'd like to take matters into your own hands and retrieve more for me from Petrus?",
	[1072726] = L"Petrus lives in Ilshenar, past the Compassion gate and beyond the gypsy camp.",
	[1072728] = L"I see. I see.  Well good luck to you.",
