	[1072262] = L"Pork is the fruit of the land!  You can barbeque it, boil it, bake it, sautee it.  There's pork kebabs, pork creole, pork gumbo, pan fried, deep fried, stir fried.  There's apple pork, peppered pork, pork soup, pork salad, pork and potatoes, pork burger, pork sandwich, pork stew, pork chops, pork loins, shredded pork.  So, let's get some piggies butchered!",
