	[1095046] = L"Red Herring",
	[1095047] = L"You take the Red Herring and put it into your pack.  The only thing more surprising than the fact that there is a fish called the Red Herring is the fact that you fished for it!",
	[1095048] = L"Oh, this good Red Herring.  Now Barreraak get to be new King of Gray Goblins.  You killed the old King when you first came here.  As new King, Barreraak give you special ring.  This ring make you better at killing goblins that say Barreraak not new King.",
